text: Mokati Stadium is a stadium in Otjiwarongo, Namibia. It is the home stadium of Mighty Gunners and Life Fighters, who play in the Namibia Premier League.Life Fighters return to Premiere League The Namibian, 2016-03-13 Mokati is situated in the suburb of Orwetoveni. ==References== Category:Otjiwarongo Category:Sports venues in Namibia Category:Football venues in Namibia Category:Buildings and structures in Otjozondjupa Region
